data.description: Settle into your cute starter home in Kathleen.  This three bedroom two bath home offers fresh paint on the walls, no carpet, large master suite and great living space.  So many layout options in the living room for all your furniture.  The back yard offers an enclosed porch, and deck outside for all your entertaining. Fully fenced and ready for it's new owners.  Come take a look!
